Title: The life of displace extremist in an unknow destination
DateModified: '2018-02-15'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/the-life-of-displace-extremist-in-an-unknow-destination-2
SetInCountry: Tanzania
Category: A decision that pushed me to the edge
AuthorName: osagie ayere
AuthorCountry: Tanzania
Text: 'My extremist act that flee me out of my country of dormiciliary were a lost
  my guardian and all properties and belonging gone in the processed which left me
  to life undesirable life with extreme hard life in the refugee camp.

  Lacking good water,facilities,poor amenities, bad treatment, agitation in the camp
  with different kind of torture and maltreated which has make life unbearable.

  I was force migrant life in the forest where i struggle to take online course in
  mechanical engineering at the unpleasant situation befallen me to see if i can redirected
  my life to a better one via this perspective.

  I can say this it wasn''t easy because of so many challenges like conflict within
  the refugee camps,demonstration,lack of food,poor accomodation,isolation and language
  barrier as keep my life in a sad and bad mood.'
